        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_WHEN                      = 10881,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. When One Man Is Not Enough(pt.1). When One Man Is Not Enough(pt.2). A Feast for Gnats(pt.1). A Feast for Gnats(pt.2). Say It with a Handbag(pt.1). Say It with a Handbag(pt.2). Say It with a Handbag(pt.3). Say It with a Handbag(pt.4). The Long March North. The Forbidden Path(pt.1). The Forbidden Path(pt.2). The Forbidden Path(pt.3). The Forbidden Path(pt.4). The Forbidden Path(pt.5). The Forbidden Path(pt.6). The Young and the Threadless(pt.1). The Young and the Threadless(pt.2). The Young and the Threadless(pt.3). Sins of the Mothers(pt.1). Sins of the Mothers(pt.2). Howl from the Heavens(pt.1). Howl from the Heavens(pt.2). Howl from the Heavens(pt.3). Manifest Destiny. At Journey's End(pt.1). At Journey's End(pt.2).
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_HER                       = 10882,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Her Memories: Verdure Footfalls(pt.1). Her Memories: Verdure Footfalls(pt.2). Her Memories: Verdure Footfalls(pt.3). Drafted by the Duchy. Battle on a New Front. Trust (Romaa Mihgo).
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING                           = 10883,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing.
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_2                         = 10884,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing.
        YOU_CAN_SET_THIS_AS_YOUR_CURRENT_HOME                                 = 10885,  -- You can set this as your current home point. Once you set a home point, you will return there whenever you are incapacitated.
