        YOUR_LIST_OF_FAVORITE_LOCATIONS_IS_FULL_YOU                           = 10905,  -- Your list of favorite locations is full. You must delete an existing entry in order to register a new one.
        DELETE_WHICH_NONE_OF_THESE                                            = 10906,  -- Delete which? None of these. % ##. % ##. % ##. % ##. % ##. % ##. % ##. % ##. % ##.
        SWIFTY_WIFTY_AND_SAFEY_WAFEY_PARCEL_DELIVERY_IS                       = 10907,  -- Swifty-wifty and safey-wafey parcel delivery! Is there something you need to send?
        A_POTENT_SPELLY_WELL_OR_TWO_CAN_BE                                    = 10908,  -- A potent spelly-well or two can be the key to survival in this time of war. But can you mastaru my magic, or will it master you?
        WELCOME_TO_THE_OPTISTERY_WE_ARE_ONE_OF                                = 10909,  -- Welcome to the Optistery. We are one of the world's largest repositories of knowledge and wisdom, housing an unmatched collection of tomes, scrolls, scriptures, chronicles, records, atlases, and just about any other type of printed material you could think of! But...
        WE_ARE_TEMPORARILY_CLOSED_DUE_TO_MINISTER_KARAHA                      = 10910,  -- We are temporarily closed due to Minister Karaha-Baruha's absence. Our deepest apologies for any inconvenience.
        I_VE_COME_FROM_SAN_D_ORIA_AS                                          = 10911,  -- I've come from San d'Oria as part of the military relief effort...
        BUT_WINDURST_IS_IN_WORSE_SHAPE_THAN_I                                 = 10912,  -- But Windurst is in worse shape than I had imagined. Such devastation... It tears at one's heart to see such a beautiful city laid to such ruin.
        I_VE_COME_FROM_BASTOK_ON_BUSINESS_BUT                                 = 10913,  -- I've come from Bastok on business, but word had not reached us of the scale of devastation here.
        IT_MUST_HAVE_BEEN_A_TERRIBLE_ORDEAL_TO                                = 10914,  -- It must have been a terrible ordeal... To think of all those little Tarutarus fighting desperately to protect their home.
        THIS_IS_THE_HUNTSMAN_S_COURT_FOR_GENERATIONS                          = 10915,  -- This is the Huntsman's Court. For generations now it has been a gathering place for Mithran rangers to sell their catches.
        BUT_NOW_IT_HAS_BECOME_A_MAKESHIFT_BARRACKS                            = 10916,  -- But now it has become a makeshift barracks for the Mithra Mercenaries.
        THE_TIMBRE_TIMBERS_TAVERN_AND_THE_RARAB_TAIL                          = 10917,  -- The Timbre Timbers Tavern and the Rarab Tail Hostelry have been closed since the outbreak of hostilities with the Yagudo began.
        NOT_BEING_ABLE_TO_EAT_AT_WINDURST_S                                   = 10918,  -- Not being able to eat at Windurst's two finest dining restaurantarus...
        THAT_S_ALMOST_AS_BAD_AS_THE_YAGUDO                                    = 10919,  -- That's almost as bad as the Yagudo siege!
        JUST_BETWEEN_YOU_AND_ME_WORD_AROUND_TOWN                              = 10920,  -- Just between you and me, word around town has it that there is some shady-wady research going on at the Rhinostery.
        LIKE_AGRO_ENGINEERING_CARNIVOROUS_PLANTS_TO_BE_USED                   = 10921,  -- Like agro-engineering carnivorous plants to be used in battle! Who would have thunk...?
        THOSE_TRADITIONALLY_REFERRED_TO_AS_WISE_WIZARDS_IN                    = 10922,  -- Those traditionally referred to as Wise Wizards in the Federation have been commissioned to lead units in battle and draw up wartime strategies.
        WE_MILITARY_SCHOLARS_HAVE_ALSO_BEEN_APPOINTED_AS                      = 10923,  -- We military scholars have also been appointed as staff officers and are serving here in Windurst as well.
        SEE_I_VE_GOT_ONE_MORRRE_THAN_YOU                                      = 10924,  -- See? I've got one morrre than you!
        OH_MY_FRIEND_AND_I_ARE_JUST_HAVING                                    = 10925,  -- Oh, my friend and I are just having a friendly competition to see who can fell the most Yagudo. The loser has to treat the winner to a year's supply of sarrrdines!
        ONE_TWO_THREE_HM_WAIT_A_MINUTE_SOMETHING                              = 10926,  -- One...two...three.. Hm? Wait a minute, something's not rrright...
        ALRIGHT_I_M_GONNA_COUNT_OVER_GIMME_A                                  = 10927,  -- Alright, I'm gonna count over. Gimme a minute here...
        THEY_SAY_A_SHADOWY_FIGURE_APPEARED_SUDDENLY_IN                        = 10928,  -- They say a shadowy figure appeared suddenly in Valdeaunia, the beastman-held lands to the north.
        BUT_WHO_COULD_POSSIBLY_BE_POWERFUL_ENOUGH_TO                          = 10929,  -- But who could possibly be powerful enough to bring the entire Yagudo Theomilitary under his control?
        I_AM_A_MEMBER_OF_THE_WILDCATS_UNDERRR                                 = 10930,  -- I am a member of the Wildcats, underrr the able command of General Haja Zhwan.
        HAVE_YOU_EVER_SEEN_HER_IN_ACTION_ON                                   = 10931,  -- Have you ever seen her in action on the field of battle? Her crossbow never misses its tarrrget!
        IT_SEEMS_THOSE_DISGUSTING_MAWS_HAVE_APPEARED_IN                       = 10932,  -- It seems those disgusting maws have appeared in several rrregions. Have you seen one yet?
        NYAAA_JUST_THINKING_ABOUT_THEM_MAKES_MY_FURRR                         = 10933,  -- Nyaaa, just thinking about them makes my furrr stand on end.
        ALL_OF_THE_MERCENARY_LEADERS_ARE_COMBAT_SPECIALISTS                   = 10934,  -- All of the mercenary leaders are combat specialists. They do it the best, do it dependably, and look good doing it! I hope I can be like one of them someday...
        IF_YOU_RE_LUCKY_ENOUGH_MAYBE_YOU_WILL                                 = 10935,  -- If you're lucky enough, maybe you will have the opporrrtunity to fight alongside them.
        A_MASTER_CASTER_IS_IN_CHARGE_OF_EACH                                  = 10936,  -- A Master Caster is in charge of each War Warlocks unit. There's Kayeel-Payeel of the Aquarian War Warlocks, and Zolku-Azolku of the Libran War Warlocks...
        A_FEW_OF_THEM_HAVE_THEIR_PECULIARITIES_BUT                            = 10937,  -- A few of them have their peculiarities, but they are all expertarus in magic!
        SIGH_I_CAN_T_BELIEVE_THAT_OUR_BEAUTIFUL                               = 10938,  -- <Sigh>... I can't believe that our beautiful city has come under attack...
        IF_ONLY_THE_PRIDE_OF_OUR_NATION_SHANTOTTO                             = 10939,  -- If only the pride of our nation, Shantotto was here... She would have nipped the situation in the bud, no doubtaru about it!
        I_HOPE_SHE_RETURNS_FROM_THE_NORTHLANDS_SOON                           = 10940,  -- I hope she returns from the northlands soon... and safely. Oh Shantotto...
        THIS_IS_THE_RHINOSTERY_HOME_TO_A_MYRIAD                               = 10941,  -- This is the Rhinostery, home to a myriad of research and study concerning all things animal and plantaru.
        UNFORTUNATELY_WITH_THE_WAY_THINGS_ARE_WE_AREN                         = 10942,  -- Unfortunately, with the way things are, we aren't able to conduct our fieldwork outside the city to the extentaru that we would like.
        WHEN_NIGHT_COMES_YOU_CAN_SEE_A_BIIIG                                  = 10943,  -- When night comes, you can see a biiig star in the sky over there. Have you seen it yet?
        EVERYONE_IS_SAYING_THAT_IT_S_SOME_SORT                                = 10944,  -- Everyone is saying that it's some sort of omen that something bad is on its way. But I can't imagine that things could get any worse than they already are.
        HEY_YOU_LISTEN_TO_THIS_IT_LL_BLOW                                     = 10945,  -- Hey, you! Listen to this. It'll blow your mind!
        NOBODY_ELSE_BELIEVES_ME_BUT_WHEN_I_WAS                                = 10946,  -- Nobody else believes me, but when I was on my way to Jeuno on business just recently, I saw a strange beastman. Like none I've ever seen before!
        IT_WAS_WEARING_A_CROWN_AND_A_LUSH                                     = 10947,  -- It was wearing a crown, and a lush mantle on its back. And it looked like...well, feline. Some kind of cat-like beastman? I can't be sure...
        THEY_SAY_THE_REASON_THE_BEASTMEN_ARE_COMING                           = 10948,  -- They say the reason the beastmen are coming after us is ultimately because they are after crystals.
        BUT_I_DON_T_SEE_WHY_THEY_HAVE                                         = 10949,  -- But I don't see why they have to get so worked up over it. If it's that big a deal to them, let's just give them some crystals. Why do they have to go and wreck our city?
        JUST_TAKE_A_LOOK_AROUND_YOU_THE_CITY                                  = 10950,  -- Just take a look around you... The city sustained significant damage during the Theomilitary's assault the other day.
        ONLY_THIS_DISTRICT_HAS_BEEN_SOMEWHAT_REPAIRED_SINCE                   = 10951,  -- Only this district has been somewhat repaired since then. Windurst Walls still remains in ruins, almost totally submerged beneath the waters.
        IT_WAS_WARLOCK_WARLORD_ROBEL_AKBEL_S_IDEA                             = 10952,  -- It was Warlock Warlord Robel-Akbel's idea to bring together all of the Federation's forces.
        EVEN_SO_NONE_OF_US_AFFILIATED_WITH_THE                                = 10953,  -- Even so, none of us affiliated with the military have even seen Robel-Akbel... Some of us have begun to question whether or not he even exists!
        THEY_SAY_THIS_DETESTABLE_YAGUDO_THEOMILITARY_IS_LED                   = 10954,  -- They say this detestable Yagudo Theomilitary is led by one named Tzee Xicu the Manifest.
        HE_MARSHALS_THE_THRONGS_OF_YAGUDO_FROM_THE                            = 10955,  -- He marshals the throngs of Yagudo from the foul depths of Castle Oztroja. There are some rumors, however, that he is actually a she.
        THE_DEVELOPMENT_OF_VARIOUS_FORMS_OF_MAGIC_HAS                         = 10956,  -- The development of various forms of magic has been well underway since the onset of hostilities.
        SOME_ARE_EVEN_BEGINNING_TO_DABBLE_AGAIN_IN                            = 10957,  -- Some are even beginning to dabble again in arts condemned as taboo in former days. Well, that's all just hearsay...
        HAVE_YOU_EVER_MET_ROMAA_MIHGO_SHE_HEADS                               = 10958,  -- Have you ever met Romaa Mihgo? She heads the Cobras, the strongest and most ruthless division of the Mithra Mercenaries.
        HER_BEHAVIOR_MAY_BE_A_BIT_NOT_TO                                      = 10959,  -- Her behavior may be a bit...not to some's liking. But her prowess is virtually without match. Windurst owes her a great debt of gratitude for her service.
        ODDLY_ENOUGH_THOUGH_IT_SEEMS_ROMAA_MIHGO_ISN                          = 10960,  -- Oddly enough, though, it seems Romaa Mihgo isn't exactly a fan of the Federation. I wonder what it was that convinced her to pledge herself to our cause...
        SIGH_TO_HAVE_COME_ALL_THE_WAY_FROM                                    = 10961,  -- <Sigh>... To have come all the way from Olzhirya to Windurst just to be met by this scene of destruction... But we must remain firm.
        THEY_SAY_THE_WEAKENING_OF_A_NATION_IS                                 = 10962,  -- They say the weakening of a nation is generally the result of its leadership. I don't know what the Star Sibyl or whoever is running Windurrrst is up to...
        STRENGTH_IS_EVERRRYTHING_TO_US_MITHRA_A_LEADER                        = 10963,  -- Strength is everrrything to us Mithra. A leader without strength is no leader at all.
        ADVENTURER_DO_YOU_KNOW_WARLOCK_WARLORD_ROBEL_AKBEL                    = 10964,  -- Adventurer, do you know Warlock Warlord Robel-Akbel? I was able to catch only a glimpse of him at the most recent battle.
        HE_WAS_WIELDING_THE_MOST_POWERFUL_MAGIC_I                             = 10965,  -- He was wielding the most powerful magic I have ever seen! He felled some one hundred Yagudo in the blink of an eye!
        I_D_GIVE_ANYTHING_TO_BE_THAT_POWERFUL                                 = 10966,  -- I'd give anything to be that powerful...
        YES_I_M_A_MITHRA_MERCENARY_DO_YOU                                     = 10967,  -- Yes, I'm a Mithra Mercenary. Do you know of my unit, adventurer? The Anacondas. Led by the grrreat Perih Vashai.
        SHE_IS_A_MASTER_OF_THE_BOW_AND                                        = 10968,  -- She is a master of the bow. And not only strong, but smarrrt as a whip to boot. There aren't many leaders these days so trusted by their troops as she.
        THE_LAST_YAGUDO_ASSAULT_A_FEW_DAYS_AGO                                = 10969,  -- The last Yagudo assault a few days ago was an absolute nightmare.
        THE_SINISTER_THEOMILITARY_FORCES_WERE_UPON_US_IN                      = 10970,  -- The sinister Theomilitary forces were upon us in an instant, an enveloping storm of pitch-black feathers ravaging the city. The horrible vision does not leave me...even in my sleep.
        CAPRICORNIAN_MASTER_CASTER_ZONPA_ZIPPA_DEVELOPED_THE_CARDIANS         = 10971,  -- Capricornian Master Caster Zonpa-Zippa developed the Cardians as a way to compensate for the Federation's lack of hardened, crack frontline troops.
        THEY_STILL_AREN_T_ENTIRELY_READY_FOR_ALL                              = 10972,  -- They still aren't entirely ready for all the applications that we'd like, but they may become capable of handling some simple tasks soon enough.
        JUST_AHEAD_IS_THE_AURASTERY_WINDURST_S_INSTITUTE                      = 10973,  -- Just ahead is the Aurastery, Windurst's institute of magic education.
        IT_IS_MOST_IMPORTANTARU_THAT_WE_SPARE_NO                              = 10974,  -- It is most importantaru that we spare no effort in educating our younger generation in our traditional magic. Especially in times such as these...
        TODAY_CLASS_WE_WILL_BE_REVIEWING_THE_BASICS                           = 10975,  -- Today, class, we will be reviewing the basics of healing magic.
        NOW_PLEASE_LISTEN_AND_REPEAT_AFTER_ME_C                               = 10976,  -- Now please listen and repeat after me. C-U-R-E. Cure.
        WHEN_I_GROW_UP_I_M_GONNA_BE                                           = 10977,  -- When I grow up, I'm gonna be the biggest Warlock Warlord ever!
        DO_YOU_KNOW_WHAT_A_WARLORD_IS_I                                       = 10978,  -- Do you know what a warlord is? I'm not quite sure...but it sure sounds really importantaru, right!?
        AT_FIRST_WHEN_THE_BIRDMEN_ATTACKED_I_WAS                              = 10979,  -- At first, when the birdmen attacked, I was just really scared... I didn't know what to do.
        BUT_THEN_I_REALIZED_THAT_I_HAD_TO                                     = 10980,  -- But then I realized that I had to fight for my Windurst. So I stayed behind all the grownups and kept casting the cure spell that my teacher taught me on them.
        I_WAS_SO_HAPPY_WAPPY_TO_SEE_MY                                        = 10981,  -- I was so happy-wappy to see my spells making some of them feel better rightaru away!
        PEOPLE_TEND_TO_FORGET_BUT_THE_REAL_REASON                             = 10982,  -- People tend to forget, but the real reason that the minister of the Optistery has cooped himself up in the Toraimarai Canal is to save Windurst from the very danger that threatens its existence, not to escape it.
        ALL_ALONE_IN_THAT_CREEPY_WEEPY_DARK_PLACE                             = 10983,  -- All alone in that creepy-weepy, dark place for days and days... I can't even imagine what it must be like.
        THIS_BRIDGE_WAS_NEARLY_OBLITERATED_IN_A_RECENT                        = 10984,  -- This bridge was nearly obliterated in a recent Yagudo attack. We just finished rebuilding it to the state that you see now.
        I_JUST_HOPE_WE_DON_TARU_HAVE_TO                                       = 10985,  -- I just hope we don'taru have to do this again...
        A_WHILE_AGO_MY_BROTHER_JOINED_THE_WAR                                 = 10986,  -- A while ago my brother joined the War Warlocks.
        EVEN_THOUGH_I_M_PROUD_THAT_HE_IS                                      = 10987,  -- Even though I'm proud that he is one of the warlock elitaru, I can't help but worry if he's alright or not...<sigh>.
        FORT_KARUGO_NARUGO_IS_OUR_STRONGHOLD_TO_THE                           = 10988,  -- Fort Karugo-Narugo is our stronghold to the north. It's absolutely essential for the defense of Windurst.
        YOU_MIGHT_EVEN_GO_SO_FAR_AS_TO                                        = 10989,  -- You might even go so far as to call it the jewel in the crown that is Windurst's magical defense against the Yagudo invasion...I'm sorry, that was a bit much...
        MEEEOOOW_THEY_SAY_IT_S_DANGERRROUS_HERE_BUT                           = 10990,  -- Meeeooow... They say it's dangerrrous here, but I can't leave without my mama! Have you seen her anywhere, mister/lady]?
        MAMA_IS_BIG_AND_STRRRONG_AND_LOVES_ME                                 = 10991,  -- Mama is big and strrrong, and loves me more than anyone in the whole wide world. I know she'll come back soon!
        I_TRAVEL_ALL_THE_WAY_FROM_BASTOK_TO                                   = 10992,  -- I travel all the way from Bastok to peddle my wares, and now they order me off the streets? No sympathy for a businesswoman's plight, I tell you...
        BUT_I_SHOULDN_T_BE_SO_SELFISH_THE                                     = 10993,  -- But I shouldn't be so selfish. The poor Tarutaru and Mithra of this nation suffer far more than I.
        MY_MOMMY_TOLD_ME_TO_RUN_TO_WINDURST                                   = 10994,  -- My mommy told me to run to Windurst Walls before the scary-wary monsters come, but I forgotaru how to get there!
        BUT_IT_S_OKAY_MY_BROTHER_WILL_KEEP                                    = 10995,  -- But it's okay! My brother will keep us safe. He's a big-time War Warlock, you know!
        ALL_MY_FRIENDS_RAN_AND_TOOK_SHELTARU_IN                               = 10996,  -- All my friends ran and took sheltaru in Windurst Waters. Am I s'posed to go with them...?
        I_VE_NEVER_SEEN_EVERYONE_IN_SUCH_A                                    = 10997,  -- I've never seen everyone in such a panic-wanic. I don't know whether to be scared or excitarued!
        MY_TEACHY_WEACHER_SAYS_WE_NEED_TO_E                                   = 10998,  -- My teachy-weacher says we need to e-vac-u-a-taru.
        I_DON_T_KNOW_WHAT_THAT_MEANS_BUT                                      = 10999,  -- I don't know what that means, but it sure sounds fun!
