        I_DON_T_HAVE_TIME_TO_ENTERTAIN_THE                                    = 11772,  -- I don't have time to entertain the likes of you. Get out of my face.
        I_GO_WHERE_I_WANT_WHEN_I_WANT                                         = 11773,  -- I go where I want, when I want. No one can take that from me. Not you, not some sibyl, not anyone.
