        HMPH_I_MIGHT_CONSIDER_HELPING_OUT_BUT_I                               = 11778,  -- Hmph... I might consider helping out [your kingdom/your republic/your federation], but I won't be making you any promises.
        HMPH_I_LL_CONSIDER_REMAINING_WITH_BUT_I                               = 11779,  -- Hmph... I'll consider remaining with [your kingdom/your republic/your federation], but I won't make you any guarantees.
        AS_YOU_CAN_SEE_I_STILL_HAVE_MANY                                      = 11780,  -- As you can see, I still have many malms to tread before my training is complete. Perhaps one day our paths will cross again on the fields of battle. Until then, friend.
