        HAS_SURVIVED_NUMERRROUS_BATTLES_AND_STARED_DEATH_IN                   = 13518,  -- % has survived numerrrous battles and stared death in the face on equal occasions. As both his/her] commander and comrrrade, I know for a fact that %'s no ordinary soldier.
