        WONDERFUL_YOU_WON_T_REGRET_IT_WITH_THIS                               = 13553,  -- Wonderful! You won't regret it. With this, the treasure is as good as yours!
        I_M_AFRAID_YOU_HAVEN_T_ENOUGH_ALLIED                                  = 13554,  -- I'm afraid you haven't enough Allied Notes...
        I_D_APPRECIATE_IF_YOU_COULD_SHARE_THIS                                = 13555,  -- I'd appreciate if you could share this news with your comrades as well. A chance like this doesn't come every day, you know, and word has it there's more than enough treasure to go around.
        THE_MONSTER_LURKS_WITHIN_THE_REGION_RECENTLY_BROUGHT                  = 13556,  -- The monster lurks within the region recently brought under [San d'Orian/Bastokan/Windurstian] control. Make haste, and may the Goddess protect you!
        OH_IT_S_YOU_AGAIN_LET_ME_GUESS                                        = 13557,  -- Oh, it's you again! Let me guess. You've come back for the %. Am I right or am I right?
        HOW_ABOUT_IT_RIGHT_YOU_ARE_ACTUALLY_NO                                = 13558,  -- How about it? Right you are. Actually, no...
