        WITH_THE_ENEMY_READY_TO_STRRRIKE_AT_ANY                               = 13568,  -- With the enemy ready to strrrike at any moment, one can never be too ready. Have you seen to your preparations?
        NEED_YOU_EVEN_ASK_WHY_AJIDO_MARUJIDO_CHILD                            = 13569,  -- Need you even ask!? Why, Ajido-Marujido, Child Genius, is ever ready for anything those filthy-wilthy-feathered goons could throw at us!
        WHAT_THE_ARE_YOU_OUT_OF_YOUR_GOURRRD                                  = 13570,  -- What the--!? Are you out of your gourrrd, you little brat!? Get back inside! If the city comes under attack, you'll break more than just the rims of those rrridiculous glasses!
