        AT_ANY_RATE_YOU_D_BEST_HURRRY_ALONG                                   = 13579,  -- At any rate, %, you'd best hurrry along. Master Lehko's waiting in Heavens Tower, and I hear he has an especially imporrrtant assignment for you this time.
        YOU_RRRE_STILL_STANDING_AROUND_HERE_MASTER_LEHKO                      = 13580,  -- %! You'rrre still standing around here? Master Lehko's waiting for you in Heavens Tower with a special assignment. Now hurry along!
        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_OUR_STALWART_YOU                                     = 13581,  -- Well, if it isn't our stalwart %! You're always a sightaru for sore eyes.
        WITH_THE_BEASTMEN_DRAWING_EVER_NEARER_IT_S                            = 13582,  -- With the beastmen drawing ever nearer, it's absolutaru madness around here. But please, don't let me keepy-weep you. Master Lehko awaits within.
