        THE_POWER_THAT_SEETHES_WITHIN_THE_BOW_OF                              = 13624,  -- The power that seethes within the Bow of Light is no ordinary power. It is a force that reaches to the very depths of our souls to wrest forth the fear, the ugliness, that we would deny is there.
        JEALOUSY_DECEIT_HATRRRED_THE_EVILS_THAT_LIE_DORMANT                   = 13625,  -- Jealousy, deceit, hatrrred... The evils that lie dormant within all of us are rrroused and brought to the fore, and we are powerless to resist.
        POWERLESS_INDEED                                                      = 13626,  -- Powerless indeed...
        BEFORE_WE_COULD_REALIZE_WHERE_WE_WENT_ASTRRRAY                        = 13627,  -- Before we could realize where we went astrrray, our verdant home was bathed in the crrrimson of our own blood. Time-nurtured bonds between sister and sister rrripped to shreds like so many scraps of cloth...
        YOW_RABNTAH_WAS_DEEMED_A_SINNER_FOR_HAVING                            = 13628,  -- Yow Rabntah was deemed a sinner for having brought this calamity upon us, and tried for her crimes. As fate would have it, she met her end at the hand of a fiend before her judgment could be passed.
        ID_13629                                                              = 13629,  -- ...
        AS_CHIEFTAINNESS_I_SHARED_RESPONSIBILITY_FOR_THE_SLAUGHTER            = 13630,  -- As Chieftainness, I shared responsibility for the slaughter, and for this sin they hunt me to this very day. Even my daughter--guilty of naught but sharrring my blood--is forced to live the life of a fugitive.
        A_TALE_TO_TUG_AT_THE_HEARTSTRRRINGS_IS                                = 13631,  -- A tale to tug at the heartstrrrings, is it not, %? I thought that by bringing Nhev and Syu to our shores, they could finally live out their lives in peace.
        SADLY_THE_PREDATOR_IS_NOT_SO_EASILY_THROWN                            = 13632,  -- Sadly, the predator is not so easily thrown off the scent. You're acquainted with the Mithran Tracker Shikaree G, are you not? Dispatched from the homeland, she continues to hunt her prrrey with an implacable tenacity that borders on obsession.
        WAS_IT_I_SHARE_WITH_YOU_MY_TALE                                       = 13633,  -- %, was it? I share with you my tale because Lehko assures me that you are a friend. Pray do not betrrray our trust.
        THIS_I_SHALL_TAKE_INTO_MY_CARE                                        = 13634,  -- This, I shall take into my care.
        IT_S_MY_DUTY_AS_MUCH_AS_YOURS                                         = 13635,  -- It's my duty as much as yours to see this dark chapter of our people's historrry to a fitting end.
        BUT_LEHKO                                                             = 13636,  -- But Lehko--
        HAVE_NO_FEAR_NHEV_REALIZING_THE_ERROR_OF                              = 13637,  -- Have no fear, Nhev. Realizing the error of her ways, Yow Rabntah with her dying breath wove a potent incantation to seal the terrible power deep within her creation.
        THAT_SUCH_MEANINGLESS_BLOODSHED_WOULD_NEVER_AGAIN_BE                  = 13638,  -- That such meaningless bloodshed would never again be visited on her prrrecious people...
        THE_SECRET_TO_UNDOING_THE_SEAL_SHE_CARRIED                            = 13639,  -- The secret to undoing the seal, she carried to her grrrave. The bow rrremains, but there is not a living soul who can release its power. Is this not so?
        AYE_YOU_VE_THE_RRRIGHT_OF_IT                                          = 13640,  -- Aye, you've the rrright of it.
        VERY_WELL_I_WAS_PREPARED_TO_DISPOSE_OF                                = 13641,  -- Very well. I was prepared to dispose of it by my own hand, but the task is yours if you would have it. Syu and I have a long road ahead of us still, and 'tis perhaps best we keep the burrrden light.
        INDEED_BEST_THE_TWO_OF_YOU_FIND_SOMEWHERRRE                           = 13642,  -- Indeed. Best the two of you find somewherrre to lie low until the fighting is through. The battlefield that awaits us will be no place for a child...
        I_VE_ORDERED_ALL_FAMILIES_IN_THE_CITY                                 = 13643,  -- I've ordered all families in the city to take up shelter in Windurst Walls. You're more than welcome to a spot among them.
        NO_YOUR_OFFER_IS_KIND_BUT_WE_MUST                                     = 13644,  -- No. Your offer is kind, but we must press on. With the Tracker on the prowl, this place is not safe for us.
        WE_MAKE_FOR_A_CITY_CALLED_JEUNO                                       = 13645,  -- We make for a city called Jeuno.
        A_SOUND_CHOICE_THE_DUCHY_IS_VAST_WITH                                 = 13646,  -- A sound choice. The Duchy is vast, with a citizenry as diverrrse as it is numerous. If there is any place you might succeed in disguising your tracks, it would be there.
        IF_I_COULD_TRRROUBLE_YOU_TO_ESCORT_OUR                                = 13647,  -- %, if I could trrrouble you to escort our guests to--
        THAT_WON_T_BE_NECESSARY_WE_VE_IMPOSED                                 = 13648,  -- That won't be necessary. We've imposed on your friend quite enough already.
        FOR_AS_LONG_AS_OUR_JOURNEY_CONTINUES_WE                               = 13649,  -- For as long as our journey continues, we face it on our own. Farewell, Lehko, %...and thank you.
        LEHKO_TWISTED_THOUGH_ITS_POWER_MAY_BE_THE                             = 13650,  -- ...Lehko. Twisted though its power may be, the bow can summon forth no evil that does not already reside within us.
        I_HAVE_LONG_BELIEVED_THAT_IN_THE_HANDS                                = 13651,  -- I have long believed that in the hands of one pure of heart and strong of will, it could have served its intended purpose...
        ID_13652                                                              = 13652,  -- ...
        THE_STONE_THAT_BROUGHT_RRRUIN_UPON_US_IS                              = 13653,  -- The stone that brought rrruin upon us is born of nature, as are we all. In the end, it is but a mirrror to the soul of its wielder...
        IT_IS_NOT_MY_PLACE_TO_QUESTION_THE                                    = 13654,  -- It is not my place to question the ways of the motherland. But is this truly the Mithran way? To hunt to the ends of the world those who have taken a step astrrray? No matter how true their intentions, no matter how deep their remorse?
        DO_WE_NOT_STRRRIVE_TO_LIVE_IN_HARMONY                                 = 13655,  -- Do we not strrrive to live in harmony with Mother Nature, with each other? No, it does not sit well with me...
        NOR_I_NHEV_NOR_I                                                      = 13656,  -- Nor I, Nhev... Nor I.
        WHAT_TRRRULY_IS_SIN                                                   = 13657,  -- What, trrruly, is sin?
        THOSE_WHO_JUDGE_US_HAVE_FOUND_THEIR_ANSWER                            = 13658,  -- Those who judge us have found their answer. Perhaps someday we sinners will find an answer of our own.
        WHAT_S_THE_MATTER_YOU_LOOK_AS_IF                                      = 13659,  -- What's the matter, %? You look as if you've seen a ghost. Fear not, for this is one bow I haven't the power to bend.
        STILL_IT_NEVER_HURTS_TO_KEEP_A_FEW                                    = 13660,  -- Still, it never hurts to keep a few powerful pieces on hand as the endgame draws near...don't you think?
        AH_HA_BUT_I_JEST_NO_THIS_BOW                                          = 13661,  -- Ah ha, but I jest. No, this bow just holds a cerrrtain sentimental value to me, you see. Given the chance, I simply couldn't let it go.
        AT_ANY_RRRATE_YOU_VE_PROVEN_YOURSELF_A                                = 13662,  -- At any rrrate, you've proven yourself a loyal friend and ally once more. Here, have this % for your trrroubles.
        MEOW_I_VE_GOT_A_PRESENT_FOR_MY                                        = 13663,  -- Meow! I've got a present for my bestest friend! You'll take it, won't you? Pretty pretty please?
        MEOWMMY_AND_I_ARE_GOING_TO_A_PLACE                                    = 13664,  -- Meowmmy and I are going to a place called Jeuno! Come visit us someday, okay?
        OH_FINISHED_YOUR_BUSINESS_WITH_MASTER_LEHKO_I                         = 13665,  -- Oh, %! Finished your business with Master Lehko, I see.
        HM_FRRRIENDS_OF_YOURS                                                 = 13666,  -- Hm? Frrriends of yours, %?
        CURIOUS_I_VE_NOT_SEEN_THEIR_FACES_BEFORE                              = 13667,  -- Curious. I've not seen their faces before...
        HAIL_MERRRCHANT_WHERE_DOES_THE_ROAD_LEAD_YOU                          = 13668,  -- Hail, merrrchant! Where does the road lead you?
        WE_STRRRIKE_FOR_JEUNO                                                 = 13669,  -- We strrrike for Jeuno.
        THE_DUCHY_LIES_IN_SHAMBLES_AFTER_THE_RECENT                           = 13670,  -- The Duchy lies in shambles after the recent beastman attack. Homes rrrazed to the ground, families huddling in the streets as they forrrage for what scraps of food they can find.
        THOUGH_I_FEEL_FOR_THEIR_PLIGHT_I_CANNOT                               = 13671,  -- Though I feel for their plight, I cannot deny that it makes for prrrofitable times for those in my trade. I've even received a substantial order directly from the Ducal Army.
        AN_ERRAND_CALLS_US_TO_JEUNO_AS_WELL                                   = 13672,  -- An errand calls us to Jeuno as well. Could we trrrouble you to take us along?
        AS_YOU_SEE_I_TRAVEL_WITH_MY_CHILD                                     = 13673,  -- As you see, I travel with my child, and the roads these days are not safe for one of her tenderrr years.
        CERRRTAINLY_I_D_WELCOME_THE_COMPANY_YOU_RE                            = 13674,  -- Cerrrtainly! I'd welcome the company. You're a cute little one, aren't ya?
        MEOW_7                                                                = 13675,  -- Meow!
        I_HAVE_YOU_THIS_TIME_SINNER                                           = 13676,  -- I have you this time...sinner!
        THAT_GARB_A_MITHRAN_TRACKER                                           = 13677,  -- That garb...! A Mithran Tracker!?
        WHAT                                                                  = 13678,  -- What--!?
        WELL_WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_PERIH_OF                                        = 13679,  -- Well, well. If it isn't Perih of the Azure Bow. Still drrragging your paws in this wrrretched backwater, I see.
        WHEN_WILL_YOU_COME_TO_YOUR_SENSES_AND                                 = 13680,  -- When will you come to your senses and go home to Elshimo? You know that this land holds nothing for you save death and sufferrring.
        YOUR_CONCERN_IS_TOUCHING_BUT_IT_WAS_ALWAYS                            = 13681,  -- Your concern is touching, but it was always a bit too sweltry there for my liking. The more temperrrate climes on these shores suit me.
        HMPH_I_SHALL_RETURN_FOR_YOU_ANOTHER_DAY                               = 13682,  -- Hmph. I shall return for you another day. Today, I pursue more urrrgent quarry...
        SHIKAREE_SHE_SAYS_SHE_S_FOUND_THE_SINNER                              = 13683,  -- Shikaree... She says she's found the sinner...?
        WAIT_A_MINUTE_LEHKO_LEHKO_HABHOKA                                     = 13684,  -- Wait a minute... Lehko...? Lehko Habhoka!
        THAT_DAY_TEN_YEARS_AGO_COULD_HE_BE                                    = 13685,  -- That day, ten years ago... Could he be...the son!?
        PERIH_WHAT_S_GOTTEN_INTO_YOU_ALL_OF                                   = 13686,  -- Perih? What's gotten into you all of a sudden?
        LEHKO_HABHOKA_WHAT_IS_IT_YOU_TRRRULY_SEEK                             = 13687,  -- Lehko Habhoka... What is it you trrruly seek?
        DRRROP_SOME_OF_THAT_STUFF_YOU_RE_CARRYING                             = 13688,  -- %! Drrrop some of that stuff you're carrying and take this % off my hands already, will ya? What in the world could this be used for, anyway...?
        OH_LEHKO_WANTED_ME_TO_GIVE_YOU_THIS                                   = 13689,  -- Oh, %. Lehko wanted me to give you this % as a reward for your brrravery. Lighten your burden and take it, will ya? And rest up while you can. Our fierrrcest battle still awaits.
        THERE_YOU_ARE_I_VE_BEEN_SCOURING_THE                                  = 13691,  -- There you are, %! I've been scouring the streets for hourrrs trying to find you!
        THE_WARLOCK_WARLORD_AND_HIS_RECONNAISSANCE_SQUAD_HAVE                 = 13692,  -- The Warlock Warlord and his reconnaissance squad have just returned bearing grrrim news from Valdeaunia.
        HE_S_ABOUT_TO_HOLD_AN_URRRGENT_DEFENSE                                = 13693,  -- He's about to hold an urrrgent defense briefing, and all mercenaries have been summoned to--
        I_REPEATARU_BY_DECREE_OF_THE_WARLOCK_WARLORD                          = 13694,  -- ...I repeataru, by decree of the Warlock Warlord, a state of emergency has been declared for all wards of the capital.
        CIVILIANS_STAY_CALM_DO_NOT_PANIC_AND_PROCEED                          = 13695,  -- Civilians: stay calm, do not panic, and proceed in an orderly-worderly fashion to the designated sheltaru in Heavens Tower. Active combatants are to report to their commanding officer for immediate briefing.
        YOU_HEARRRD_THAT_THERE_S_NOT_A_MOMENT                                 = 13696,  -- ...You hearrrd that, %. There's not a moment to lose!
        OURRR_APOLOGIES_FOR_THE_DELAY                                         = 13697,  -- Ourrr apologies for the delay.
        AND_THIS_IS_HOW_WE_STAND_TWO_ENEMY                                    = 13698,  -- ...And this is how we stand. Two enemy battalions bear down on the Federation even as we speak.
        THE_FIRST_IS_A_CADRE_OF_THE_DARK                                      = 13699,  -- The first is a cadre of the Dark Kindred, the elite guard of the Shadow Lord himself. Like the fiends that razed Karugo-Narugo, but twice as fearrrsome, if our scouts speak true.
        WE_LL_ALSO_BE_WELCOMING_A_FLOCK_OF                                    = 13700,  -- We'll also be welcoming a flock of crows to the festivities. The six regiments of the Senary Wing raise siege turrets on the outskirts of their Oztrojan nest, where they are joined by the Manifest's own Forbidden Guard.
        THEIR_MOVEMENTS_ARE_MEASURED_AND_DELIBERATE_AS_IF                     = 13701,  -- Their movements are measured and deliberate, as if each is matching the itinerary of the other. They'll be convening on the march southward, I'd wagerrr.
        IT_WILL_NOT_BE_LONG_BEFORE_THEY_ARE                                   = 13702,  -- It will not be long before they are upon us.
        BUT_TO_LAUNCH_A_PREEMPTIVE_STRIKE_WOULD_ONLY                          = 13703,  -- But to launch a preemptive strike would only deprive us of what precious few advantages we possess. No, we shall hold them here. We defend Windurst with our lives.
        THE_ENEMY_WILL_COME_BY_WAY_OF_SARUTABARUTA                            = 13704,  -- The enemy will come by way of Sarutabaruta and the port. War Warlocks. Make immediately for Windurst Waters and take formation as directed. It is there that our battle will be won.
        THE_FOE_WE_FACE_IS_UNPREDICTABLE_EVEN_SHOULD                          = 13705,  -- The foe we face is unpredictable. Even should the tide of battle seem to turn in your favor, lull yourselves not into a false sense of security, but be ever ready to adapt to the movements of your adversary.
        WE_WILL_NEED_ALL_OUR_STRRRENGTH_AND_FLAWLESS                          = 13706,  -- We will need all our strrrength and flawless cooperation to keep the Shadow Lord's fiends at bay. All Mithran Mercenary units are to join the War Warlocks and solidify the perimeter defense.
        WITH_ONE_EXCEPTION_ROMAA                                              = 13707,  -- ...With one exception. Romaa!
        ID_13708                                                              = 13708,  -- !?
        YOU_AND_YOUR_COBRAS_HAVE_PROVEN_YOURSELVES_THE                        = 13709,  -- You and your Cobras have proven yourselves the most verrrsatile of our units. I would have you on the front lines, to meet our enemy's initial charge.
        YOU_ARE_TO_TAKE_FORMATION_OUTSIDE_ODIN_S                              = 13710,  -- You are to take formation outside Odin's Gate, in West Sarutabaruta. Brrring down an enemy commander or two, disrupt their leadership and lower their morale, and the fight will be that much the easier.
        GOOD_GRRRIEF_JUST_WHEN_I_THOUGHT_YOUR_SCHEMES                         = 13711,  -- Good grrrief. Just when I thought your schemes couldn't get any more rrreckless.
        YOU_OBJECT                                                            = 13712,  -- You object?
        NAH_WE_WOULDN_T_HAVE_IT_ANY_OTHER                                     = 13713,  -- Nah, we wouldn't have it any other way! Rrright, girls!?
        VERY_WELL_THEN_YOU_HAVE_YOUR_ORDERS_HM                                = 13714,  -- Very well. Then you have your orders--hm?
        AH_BEGGING_WEGGING_YOUR_PARDON_SIRS                                   = 13715,  -- Ah! Begging-wegging your pardon, sirs...
        WHAT_IS_THIS_INTRRRUSION_THIS_IS_A_CONFIDENTIAL                       = 13716,  -- What is this intrrrusion? This is a confidential briefing!
        TRULY_WULY_SORRY_I_AM_M_MASTER_LEHKO                                  = 13717,  -- Truly-wuly sorry I am, M-Master Lehko, sir. It's justaru that... It's Minister Karaha-Baruha, sir. He's...surfaced.
        ID_13718                                                              = 13718,  -- !?
        LEAD_HIM_IN_AT_ONCE                                                   = 13719,  -- Lead him in at once!
        IT_S_REALLY_HIM                                                       = 13720,  -- It's really him...!
        EGADS_HE_S_AS_PALE_AS_A_WIGHTARU                                      = 13721,  -- Egads! He's as pale as a wightaru...
        WELL_MET_FRIENDS_I_AM_SORRY_IF_MY                                     = 13722,  -- Well met, friends! I am sorry if my extended absence has caused undue concern.
        WHAT_S_THIS_THE_HERMIT_MINISTER_LIVES_YOU                             = 13723,  -- What's this!? The hermit minister lives!? You were cooped up in that musty-wusty laboratory of yours for so long I figured there was nothing left of you but dustaru and robes!
        ALWAYS_A_PLEASURE_TO_SEE_YOU_AS_WELL                                  = 13724,  -- Always a pleasure to see you as well, Zonpa-Zippa! And what of your Cardians? Are they ready for battle?
        BWAHAHAHA_IT_WOULD_SEEM_THE_MOLDY_WOLD_ON                             = 13725,  -- Bwahahaha! It would seem the moldy-wold on your cap has gone straight to your brain! You should know that the prodigious intellect of the great Zonpa-Zippa knows no limitaru! A stronger army of automata the world has never seen!
        WARLOCK_WARLORD_IT_IS_MY_PLEASURE_TO_ANNOUNCE                         = 13726,  -- Warlock Warlord. It is my pleasure to announce that my research, at long last, reaches completion.
        EXCELLENT_WE_HAVE_BUT_A_MOMENT_OF_CALM                                = 13727,  -- Excellent. We have but a moment of calm before the storm. Rest your mind, and ready yourself fully for the task ahead.
        VERY_WELL_YOU_ALL_HAVE_YOUR_ORDERS_TO                                 = 13728,  -- Very well. You all have your orders. To your positions! Dismissed!
        A_MOMENT_2                                                            = 13729,  -- A moment, %.
        YOUR_QUESTIONING_GAZE_HAS_NOT_ESCAPED_ME                              = 13730,  -- Your questioning gaze has not escaped me.
        I_WILL_NOT_ASK_WHAT_YOU_MAY_HAVE                                      = 13731,  -- I will not ask what you may have seen. No, I ask you only to trust me, %.
        PLACE_YOUR_TRUST_IN_ROBEL_AKBEL_I_SHALL                               = 13732,  -- Place your trust in Robel-Akbel? I shall, unwaveringly. ...
        YOU_HAVE_MY_THANKS_LISTEN_WELL_FOR_THIS                               = 13733,  -- You have my thanks. Listen well, for this will be the last request I make of you.
        I_SEE_THEN_DO_THIS_NOT_FOR_ME                                         = 13734,  -- ...I see. Then do this not for me, but for Windurst. In either event, it will be the last request I make of you.
        YOU_ARE_I_IMAGINE_ACQUAINTED_WITH_MAGICITE                            = 13735,  -- You are, I imagine, acquainted with magicite.
        PERHAPS_IN_YOUR_TRAVELS_YOU_HAVE_ACQUAINTED_YOURSELF                  = 13736,  -- Perhaps, in your travels, you have acquainted yourself with a substance called magicite.
        RESEMBLING_A_CRYSTAL_BUT_POSSESSING_A_POWER_EVEN                      = 13737,  -- Resembling a crystal, but possessing a power even more fearsome...
        I_WOULD_HAVE_YOU_DELIVER_THREE_SHARDS_OF                              = 13738,  -- %. I would have you deliver three shards of magicite here to me. %, %, and %.
        IN_CHAMBERS_DEEP_WHERE_THE_BALEFUL_SHADOWS_OF                         = 13739,  -- In chambers deep, where the baleful shadows of darkness have long since vanquished the light...it is there they lie.
        THREE_CHAMBERS_WHERE_NONE_SAVE_YOU_MAY_TRAVEL                         = 13740,  -- Three chambers where none--save you--may travel. I need not explain further.
        WHAT_PURPOSE_WILL_THEY_SERVE_BRING_THEM_TO                            = 13741,  -- What purpose will they serve? Bring them to me, and I shall see that all your questions are answered.
        I_AWAIT_YOUR_RETURN                                                   = 13742,  -- I await your return, %.
        HM_ON_ANOTHER_TOP_SECRETARU_MISSION_FOR_THE                           = 13743,  -- Hm? On another top-secretaru mission for the Warlock Warlord, are we? Something about a magic-wagic stone?
        OH_LOOKY_WOOK_WHO_S_BACK_YOU_D                                        = 13744,  -- Oh, looky-wook who's back. You'd best hurry in. Robel-Akbel's waiting for you, and we both know he's not a patientaru man!
        ID_13745                                                              = 13745,  -- %.
        I_KNOW_I_AM_NOT_AN_EASY_MASTER                                        = 13746,  -- I know I am not an easy master. Despite this, you have served me loyal and true. For this, you have my thanks.
        WE_STAND_ON_THE_EVE_OF_RECKONING_OUR                                  = 13747,  -- We stand on the eve of reckoning. Our age-old struggle with the beastmen shall draw to a close, and with it, one chapter of history. Before we go forth to meet our fates, I would share with you...my secret.
        WHAT_I_AM_ABOUT_TO_SAY_IS_KNOWN                                       = 13748,  -- What I am about to say is known to Lehko and none other. I trust you will see that it remains that way.
        IT_IS_AS_YOU_SURMISE_I_LIKE_YOU                                       = 13749,  -- It is as you surmise. I, like you, have traveled here from an age yet to come. ...From Vana'diel's future.
        BUT_THE_FUTURE_I_CALL_HOME_IS_NOT                                     = 13750,  -- But the future I call home is not the one you know. No, in my Windurst, the Star Sibyl has long since fallen to the clutches of darkness. The once-majestic branches of the Great Star Tree sag, withered and dying...
        MANY_YEARS_HAVE_I_LIVED_WITH_BITTER_REMORSE                           = 13751,  -- Many years have I lived with bitter remorse as my only companion, my heart haunted by a single thought: if only I could have saved her...
        UNTIL_BY_A_STROKE_OF_WHAT_CAN_ONLY                                    = 13752,  -- Until, by a stroke of what can only be called fortune, I found myself with the chance to return here--to the past--to set right that which had gone so terribly wrong.
        MY_LONG_AWAITED_CHANCE_TO_REWRITE_THE_PAGES                           = 13753,  -- My long-awaited chance...to rewrite the pages of history.
        ARMED_WITH_THE_KNOWLEDGE_THAT_WARLOCK_WARLORD_ROBEL                   = 13754,  -- Armed with the knowledge that Warlock Warlord Robel-Akbel fell in the First Battle of Windurst, it was no great task to take control of this nation and assume my role on this grand stage.
        THAT_HE_WAS_AN_INTENSELY_PRIVATE_MAN_KNOWN                            = 13755,  -- That he was an intensely private man known to shun public appearances made it that much the easier.
        MY_FACE_CONCEALED_I_RETURNED_FROM_THE_BATTLEFIELD                     = 13756,  -- My face concealed, I returned from the battlefield upon which he had perished. Who would think to question my identity?
        YOU_LOOK_AS_IF_YOU_HAVE_SOMETHING_TO                                  = 13757,  -- You look as if you have something to say, %. Well? Speak your mind.
        WHAT_CONCERNS_YOU_THE_ORIGINAL_ROBEL_AKBEL_YOUR                       = 13758,  -- What concerns you? The original Robel-Akbel. Your true identity.
        HE_WAS_POSSESSED_OF_GREAT_POWERS_OF_THIS                              = 13759,  -- He was possessed of great powers, of this there is no doubt. But he was perhaps a bit too trusting for his own good...
        I_CAN_SEE_THE_GEARS_TURNING_IN_YOUR                                   = 13760,  -- I can see the gears turning in your head, %.
        YOU_WOULD_BELIEVE_THAT_I_HAD_A_HAND                                   = 13761,  -- You would believe that I had a hand in his demise?
        MY_TRUE_IDENTITY_WHAT_WOULD_YOU_HAVE_ME                               = 13762,  -- ...My true identity? What would you have me say, %?
        I_AM_BUT_A_SAD_FOOL_WHO_WOULD                                         = 13763,  -- I am but a sad fool who would brandish his half-cocked schemes in an impudent rebellion against history, all for the love of a single woman. To say more would only render my humiliation complete.
        NO_MATTER_YOU_ARE_FREE_TO_SPECULATE_AS                                = 13764,  -- No matter. You are free to speculate as you wish. Such trifling details are soon to be buried deep in the sands of time.
        LET_US_RETURN_TO_THE_MATTER_AT_HAND                                   = 13765,  -- Let us return to the matter at hand. I intend to channel my own magical energies to ensure Karaha-Baruha's safety during the summoning. The magicite you brought me shall act as a conduit.
        A_SOUND_PLAN_YET_NOT_LIKELY_TO_ESCAPE                                 = 13766,  -- A sound plan, yet not likely to escape the notice of our friends from the future. No, we can expect them to do all in their power to seize the energy for their own foul purposes...
        LISTEN_TO_ME_WHEN_ALL_IS_DONE_YOU                                     = 13767,  -- %, listen to me. When all is done, you and Lehko must--
        MY_APOLOGIES_MIGHT_I_HAVE_A_MOMENT_OF                                 = 13768,  -- My apologies. Might I have a moment of your time, Warlock Warlord?
        OF_COURSE                                                             = 13769,  -- Of course.
        SO_WE_MEET_AGAIN_IT_WAS                                               = 13770,  -- ...So we meet again. %, it was?
        SUCH_A_CURIOUS_MAN_WOMAN_YOU_ARE_YES                                  = 13771,  -- Such a curious man/woman] you are. Yes, there can be no doubt...
        I_SUSPECTED_AS_MUCH_FROM_THE_MOMENT_I                                 = 13772,  -- I suspected as much from the moment I met you. You have come here from another world. No, another--
        AH_BUT_IT_HARDLY_MATTERS_NOW_NO_THERE                                 = 13773,  -- Ah, but it hardly matters now. No, there is but one thing I would ask of you...
        WHERE_YOU_HAIL_FROM_DO_THE_PEOPLE_OF                                  = 13774,  -- Where you hail from, do the people of Windurst live in happiness?
        DO_THEY_LIVE_IN_HAPPINESS_THEY_DO                                     = 13775,  -- Do they live in happiness? They do. ...
        ID_13776                                                              = 13776,  -- ...
        I_SEE_THANK_YOU_FOR_YOUR_CANDOR                                       = 13777,  -- I see. Thank you for your candor.
        THE_HOUR_DRAWS_NEAR_ROMAA_AND_THE_COBRAS                              = 13778,  -- %. The hour draws near. Romaa and the Cobras ready themselves in West Sarutabaruta as we speak. It is time you joined them.
        HOW_DO_WE_STAND_MINISTER                                              = 13779,  -- How do we stand, Minister?
        QUITE_WELL_WARLOCK_WARLORD_QUITE_WELL_I_HAVE                          = 13780,  -- Quite well, Warlock Warlord. Quite well. I have reviewed my calculations over and again, and can find no flaws of which to speak.
        NEEDLESS_TO_SAY_WITH_SUCH_A_COMPLEX_INVOCATION                        = 13781,  -- Needless to say, with such a complex invocation, there are countless variables at play. You may rest assured, though, that all possible contingencies have been accounted for.
        ABOVE_ALL_ELSE_IT_WILL_COME_DOWN_TO                                   = 13782,  -- Above all else, it will come down to my strength of spirit. Have I within me the courage to confront my most deeply held terrors and emerge with heart and mind intact?
        I_WILL_BE_FRANK_WITH_YOU_WARLOCK_WARLORD                              = 13783,  -- I will be frank with you, Warlock Warlord. I am not, by nature, a fearful man. But as I came to unravel the riddle of your identity, I became frightened--frightened to the very core of my soul.
        ID_13784                                                              = 13784,  -- ...
        I_SHOULD_HAVE_KNOWN_IT_WOULD_BE_IMPOSSIBLE                            = 13785,  -- I should have known it would be impossible to conceal the truth from you forever.
        ID_13786                                                              = 13786,  -- ...!
        YES_YES_SO_IT_IS_AS_I_THOUGHT                                         = 13787,  -- Yes...yes...so it is as I thought!
        MY_SUMMONING_OF_THE_GREAT_BEAST_DID_NOT                               = 13788,  -- My summoning of the Great Beast did not proceed as planned. I...failed us.
        I_COULD_NOT_SAVE_WINDURST_FROM_ITS_FATE                               = 13789,  -- I could not save Windurst from its fate of destruction. I...failed us.
        THIS_TIME_THOUGH_WILL_BE_DIFFERENT_WE_WILL                            = 13790,  -- This time, though, will be different. We will succeed. We must.
        OH_YES_HEARING_S_WORDS_JUST_NOW_HAS                                   = 13791,  -- Oh, yes. Hearing %'s words just now has freed me from all doubt. There can be no question. We shall emerge victorious.
        INDEED_HEARING_S_WORDS_JUST_NOW_HAS_INSTILLED                         = 13792,  -- Indeed. Hearing %'s words just now has instilled me with newfound resolve. We have no other choice.
        LET_US_WIN_BACK_OUR_RIGHTFUL_FUTURE_WARLOCK                           = 13793,  -- Let us win back our rightful future, Warlock Warlord Robel-Akbel.
        NO_I_SHOULD_SAY                                                       = 13794,  -- No. I should say--
        WARLOCK_WARLORD_SIR                                                   = 13795,  -- Warlock Warlord, sir!
        NEWS_FROM_KARUGO_NARUGO_SIR_THE_ENEMY_IS                              = 13796,  -- News from Karugo-Narugo, sir! The enemy is on the move in Aragoneu!
